{"tid":2404741,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"A酸幾時見效？爆到好灰","createTime":"2021-02-12T02:05:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T13:59:17.000Z","uid":221437,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"32d96bd63dc7cc7407186b516c10868f6a07672c","tid":2404741,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"任何你諗得出既令暗瘡好既方法我都有做（除咗我比較遲訓戒唔到）<br />\n<br />\n食左20mg+抗生素一個半月，皮膚、手、咀有乾，我感覺冇乜副作用，冇坊間講到咁恐怖，已經過左一個月既爆發期但係我仲一直係咁生石頭瘡，平均一星期生1-3粒，生好大粒好紅，試過生過尾指咁長既石頭瘡出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係度諗係爆發期未過定係隻藥冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/rubbish.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8846493e06dea6bc60f6f324d31e36ae2c50591e","tid":2404741,"uid":221437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:06:12.000Z","msg":"Po錯多次添"},{"pid":"d1a86ef06f0fb13c98818be63f30b594ae013b88","tid":2404741,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"你爆瘡爆左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e7f8f7598363e39aef8d54b0157b8bd45695e20","tid":2404741,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"我第三次食。第4個月先開始收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍下啦"},{"pid":"71ac388e1b3d94bebe8d4e0d72a42c4f9d65c3e2","tid":2404741,"uid":221437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1a86ef06f0fb13c98818be63f30b594ae013b88","tid":2404741,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"你爆瘡爆左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:12:16.000Z","msg":"八年，除咗中一之前，冇一日皮膚係白滑過"},{"pid":"f768daa6cf052c6d225dd5925c9440e112bb652c","tid":2404741,"uid":367644,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:13:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆