,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:13:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:16:07.000Z","msg":"水我每日飲1800<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我死都唔肯早訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:25:36.000Z","msg":"訓覺最有用"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"瞓覺可能幫到少少啦，不過去到食A酸，多數都係皮脂腺過分發達問題多，A酸要食到咁上下先至可以收縮到皮脂腺，咁樣先至唔會再有暗瘡。"},{"pid":"ba51bae52c0ec268e09687c7a1da5fb6ac1791f3","tid":2404741,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e7f8f7598363e39aef8d54b0157b8bd45695e20","tid":2404741,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"我第三次食。第4個月先開始收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍下啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"第三次食係因為轉醫生？"},{"pid":"55cf2838e8df42a7a1283906b30f77f155c210ec","tid":2404741,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ac388e1b3d94bebe8d4e0d72a42c4f9d65c3e2","tid":2404741,"uid":221437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1a86ef06f0fb13c98818be63f30b594ae013b88","tid":2404741,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:08:12.000Z","msg":"你爆瘡爆左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:12:16.000Z","msg":"八年，除咗中一之前，冇一日皮膚係白滑過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:33:56.000Z","msg":"八年，淨係食住A酸生過晒啲皮膚都有排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢會由底層一路清去表面<br />\n你生左八年應該底層都爛晒<br />\n慢慢黎啦"},{"pid":"50a10f99baf7da84644aa3ca739b8d2106c5198d","tid":2404741,"uid":15080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:34:50.000Z","msg":"兩年前食 30mg 一日<br />\n大約食左半年先開始有顯著效果 <br />\n成個療程食足一年<br />\n之後就斷尾 無再生 <br />\n不過副作用真係乾到爆 個嘴邊係咁裂"},{"pid":"7cafc8950d2aaa0c028a00a2901b85be7b6b38e4","tid":2404741,"uid":30666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:36:29.000Z","msg":"真係慢慢黎啦<br />\n你之後諗下全身乾到仆街點搞仲好<br />\n好快好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ccb73c5026891020e2c1d4600ab01b353573492","tid":2404741,"uid":256215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:38:48.000Z","msg":"其實石頭瘡係咪敏感？ 我以前暗瘡都多，但睇醫生話我有唔少都係敏感唔係暗瘡。<br />\n<br />\n可能因為用藥或者食物敏感，之後我完全唔查藥，經常用清水洗面，情況就好好多（雖然都有生）"},{"pid":"5782387413694da4fdce3adc2597f6d1de616433","tid":2404741,"uid":244161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:46:50.000Z","msg":"頭兩個月食40MG一日<br />\n早晚一粒20Mg，頭一個月好明顯咁停左生瘡<br />\n第二個月已經開始褪印<br />\n第三個月-第四個月開始只係朝早食一粒20Mg，依家連印都冇埋，但醫生都建議我食多兩個月20Mg，驚遲啲又會爆返<br />\n我都係爆左8年暗瘡，生活要早睡早起，飲多啲水，最忌飲甜野，出街搽防曬"},{"pid":"ddd491bb9bbdb742284a0be59287822d934738f6","tid":2404741,"uid":103238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:49:59.000Z","msg":"加油 我當年都食咗半年先見效<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n20mg per day"},{"pid":"c8075186da15fdd70a9fbce658444ee4a8eec4e9","tid":2404741,"uid":96486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba51bae52c0ec268e09687c7a1da5fb6ac1791f3","tid":2404741,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e7f8f7598363e39aef8d54b0157b8bd45695e20","tid":2404741,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:11:38.000Z","msg":"我第三次食。第4個月先開始收<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍下啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"第三次食係因為轉醫生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"完咗療程 隔一年又